{"name":"Alternative Illusions","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You cannot create @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figments} that include a visual element; you might be able to create the sound of a bear or the smell of a bear, but not the image of a bear. As your illusions do not have an appearance, passing through them does not automatically reveal them to be illusions (as they have no substance to pass through), but you also cannot blind targets or deal damage with @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.9PMsjiFA3iQI5uDN]{Potent Illusions}, as your illusions have no image or substance for anyone to interact with. You gain @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.w0uruW7YzHNEANaA]{Greater Illusions} as a bonus talent.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Spheres of Power","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Illusion Sphere","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jvc9MjSXj7pOw4bp":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.2SHuUW1t6696PefF.Item.3HmcLdSfVmmEoj0K"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685546688375,"modifiedTime":1685548839466,"lastModifiedBy":"jvc9MjSXj7pOw4bp"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"3gzJ3PhKxy9osrS1"}
{"name":"Potent Illusions","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figments} can be so powerful that they can affect creatures in many ways, even if they disbelieve them. Depending on what <strong>(sensory)</strong> talents you possess, this could include blinding lights, thunderous noise, smells so strong they induce nausea, or even fire that can kill.</p><p><strong>Augment 3 sp:</strong> Creatures who begin their turn within the area of your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} must make an [[/r 1d20 + @abilities.int.save]]{Intelligence} saving throw or be blinded for the round.</p><p><strong>Augment 1 sp:</strong> Creatures who begin their turn within the area of your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} must make an [[/r 1d20 + @abilities.int.save]]{Intelligence} saving throw or be deafened for one minute.</p><p><strong>Augment 1 sp:</strong> If you possess @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.w0uruW7YzHNEANaA]{Greater Illusions}, creatures who begin their turn within the area of your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} must make an [[/r 1d20 + @abilities.int.save]]{Intelligence} saving throw or take 1d4 psychic damage. The amount of psychic damage that a creature takes when it fails its saving throw increases by 1d4 at 5th level (2d4), 11th level (3d4), and 17th level (4d4).</p><p><strong>Augment 2 sp:</strong> If you possess @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.w0uruW7YzHNEANaA]{Greater Illusions}, creatures who begin their turn within the area of your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} must make an [[/r 1d20 + @abilities.int.save]]{Intelligence} saving throw or be poisoned for the round.</p><p><strong>Augment 2 sp:</strong> If you possess @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.fSPwuGZDlNgEqvQT]{Veiled Illusions}, creatures who begin their turn within the area of your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} must make an [[/r 1d20 + @abilities.int.save]]{Intelligence} saving throw or be frightened for the round.</p><p><strong>Augment 2 sp:</strong> If you possess Intelligent Illusions, creatures who begin their turn within the area of your @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} must make an [[/r 1d20 + @abilities.int.save]]{Intelligence} saving throw or be charmed for as long as they remain inside the @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment}. A creature who disbelieves the @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.illusion.b1XgEOuW7gWwNPPR]{figment} becomes immune to its charm effect, and the charm ends if it was being affected.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Spheres of Power","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"10","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cube"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":0},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"int","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"","components":{"vocal":false,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"cantrip","formula":"floor((@details.level + 1)/6)d4"}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jvc9MjSXj7pOw4bp":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.2SHuUW1t6696PefF.Item.ydMUY4sNQPdmG5Bs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685545766859,"modifiedTime":16